      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "A dict is \u0060: item\u0060 AND still rejects ordering \u2014 \u0060item\u0060 carries no IOrderableValue\nto leak in. sort over a list-of-dict is unorderable; PLang returns that as an error\n(not a thrown exception), so the on-error handler catches it.",
